Package Description
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.app
Provides the class for the simple command and graphic application
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.core
Provides all core classes and method to do extraction and listing of mail boxes.
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.formattools
Provides all core classes and method to deal with identification and format conversion tools .
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.javamail
Provides all classes to use JavaMail library.
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.javamail.rfc822
Provides all classes to implement a rfc822 single message container for JavaMail library.
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.javamail.thundermbox
Provides all classes to implement a Thunderbird mbox provider for JavaMail library.
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.libpst
Provides all classes to use libpst library.
fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.nodes
Provides all classes and method to create, manage and edit to disk the ArchiveUnits with their metadata.
